Package com.karusmc.xmc.xml.nodes

Provides classes that represent XML nodes used in the the Parser class in the parent package.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Node
    Functional interface which is an abstract representation of an XML node.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CommandsNode
    Represents a commands XML node.
    GenericNode
    A generic representation of an XML node that delegates parsing any encountered XMLEvents to internally stored Node and Tag instances.

Package com.karusmc.xmc.xml.nodes Description

Provides classes that represent XML nodes used in the the Parser class in the parent package. This package includes a generic, general purpose node, a node that represents a commands node and a functional interface, Node.
